com.blazegraph.gremlin.structure

Interface BlazeReifiedElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BlazeElement, org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Element
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BlazeEdge, BlazeVertexProperty, EmptyBlazeVertexProperty

    public interface BlazeReifiedElement
extends BlazeElement
    Common interface for BlazeEdge and BlazeVertexProperty, both of which use a sid (reified statement) as their RDF id for attaching labels (BlazeEdge) and properties (both).
    Author:
    mikepersonick
